Sun kissed

Sara Jeihooni – In My Bag

Exposed

Sara Jeihooni : Music Over TV Dramas Any Day

SYDNEY, NEW SOUTH WALES, AUSTRALIA, October 25, 2023 /EINPresswire.com/ — Sara Jeihooni, who is of Persian descent, has been a sensation since she joined the cast of Shahs of Sunset in 2020. The show, which is full of drama and conflict, has made her a household name.

Now, Jeihooni is moving from acting to singing, and with the release of her debut single “ In My Bag”.

Jeihooni is a new voice in music, and she’s quickly making a name for herself in the industry. With a unique sound and a passion for her work, Jeihooni is quickly becoming one of the most sought-after artists in the business.

“I’ve always loved music, and it’s something that I’ve wanted to do for a long time,” Jeihooni said. “I’m so excited to finally share my music with the world.” “It’s been really important for me to represent my culture in my music,” said Jeihooni.

Jeihooni’s motivation to succeed in the music industry is due to her mother, Fatemeh. Jeihooni describes her mother as a very classy, gracious, and elegant woman who gave her all to ensure her family had the best life while growing up in America.

“In My Bag” is a pop song with a Middle Eastern influence, and it’s about Jeihooni’s experience growing up Iranian-American.

“In My Bag” has been met with great success, reaching over 75,000 streams within its first 8 weeks. The song is a catchy, upbeat track that is sure to get stuck in your head.

Jeihooni is an artist to watch out for in the coming years. With her catchy tunes and relatable lyrics, she is sure to take the music world by storm.

“It’s been really important for me to represent my culture in my music,” Jeihooni said. “I want to show people that there’s more to Iran than what they see on the news.” . “Enjoying work you are told to do isn’t the same as doing what you love doing, to me music wasn’t work but T.V. , wow that was hard work. With music I don’t feel like I’m working, I do give it my all. I take my time, I invest I’m myself because it’s not work its living”, said Jeihooni.

It’s this passion and dedication that has led to Jeihooni’s success so far. And it’s also what sets her apart from many of her contemporaries. In a world where so many musicians are simply going through the motions, Jeihooni is a refreshing breath of fresh air.

Jeihooni is currently working on her debut album, which is set to be released later this year.

Robbie Merritt
